price: 5. Azali kokanisa ete moto moko te azali na nguya koleka ye?
arabic: أَيَحۡسَبُ أَن لَّن يَقۡدِرَ عَلَيۡهِ أَحَدٞ

version.title: Lingala translation
version.description: Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur’an into the Lingala language, translated by Zakaria Muhammad Balngogo.

meta.transliteration: ayaḥsabu an lan yaqdira ʿalayhi aḥadun
